            <title>[HTTPCLIENT-337] Move Content-Type to the RequestEntity</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HTTPCLIENT-337</link>
                <project id="12310360" key="HTTPCLIENT">HttpComponents HttpClient</project>
                        <description>The content type is really a property of the RequestEntity.  It should be moved there.</description>
